UVAT TECHNOLOGY said unconsolidated sales
in December fell 43.04% to NT$25,941,000 from NT$45,541,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  12/2011          12/2010
Sales             25,941           45,541    
YOY%             -43.04%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            545,989          534,720    
YOY%              2.11%  
=================================================================
 